column5: Link to Flyer  Deals look okay...was hoping for more deals on rods/reels, preferably spinning. No tackle (advertised anyways). I don't really need anything in the flyer but thought maybe some of you guys would like to know the deals!   Any thoughts on the BPS Enigma reel+free rod? Might be my chance to try baitcasting...
Is that CANADIAN prices? The m68 ice machine is on for $199.99 Damn now I have to make a decision, take back the x67
Yes Skeeter. The Vaughan Mills Location.
Hey Dann, that m68 isnt the portable ice machine, it looks like is just the head unit, base and probably a transducer for mounting on a boat.
My mind is set. I'm keeping the X67 ice under the tree. Well until Sunday, then it play time.

Looks like a great deal, look at the reel on their site there are plenty of reviews....for 70bucks it might be a great place to start for a beginer if you can master it or enjoy then upgrade if not your not out much coin.  As well i notice they have a new model of this reel coming out so its a clearance item now.
